{"h91d523c6g3968g4092gb42dgbbc1f886d048": ["Stop! I give up! M-mercy, please!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "96d340ba-698c-55c8-4a1c-94d49f3a32a7"], "h64a7175bg3279g440fgb586gcd69348d9144": ["I know things, if you l-let me live, I'll make it worth your while. I p-promise!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "15287c39-933a-1f27-bac3-1d4a3bf0867e"], "h7ff25eaagf519g4a22g9bc9g740041e57c59": ["Tell me where to find Spike.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "67172fc9-f57d-5211-7117-5215714f5252"], "hedd1f37dg6823g48e6g9668g56aa3d63672b": ["The c-camp. East-ways. Spike's prob'ly gettin' his jollies in the torture-cell.", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "d50f67fa-605b-d3e2-b578-f4e6c84971c5"], "h467bd909g83f0g4c72g90fag1289304b7a80": ["Now let me go. You got what you wanted!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "5ee54069-5283-3ab6-b27d-5851e634646d"], "h666c2596g3da7g4bb7g8d81gd1904b156197": ["You found a woman in a pod. Where did you take her?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "fb99a4a2-f0a7-9e0f-d088-9ead576eaeab"], "h1ae53336g7a20g45cag9bbcgf30e6a2e64c4": ["The lady Spike nabbed? Drow hauled 'er to Moonrise - jus' over the mountain pass!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "513808af-6544-2872-f7a8-9d63aa46b279"], "h5480f8aag4c05g44deg9218g992edabb3c49": ["You deserve no mercy! <i>Finish him.</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "d43eb403-04ff-8725-0410-ec2e580a130a"], "h08e12da6g8df6g46efg891dg60d4826f619c": ["N-n-noo!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "1ae5f58f-fcaf-8f21-40c0-ee26552c2b50"], "h16c39188gc88dg4990gba6ag4278168a0267": ["Get out of here. Go!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "325ff206-4f4a-b597-0735-6522c5d11370"], "h225382e0g6d01g4b46ga435g0a10f5ddbbda": ["T-thanks!  And 'pologies. And... erm... bye!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "38c932fb-6ffe-b32f-dc6f-c3654cc54e03"], "hd26c6156g6a55g47fbga45ag3eed891dd46c": ["<i>Chk. </i>I'd have slit his throat and drank the drippings.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "accb5260-9bcd-fa02-efb3-c661bf944c74"], "h0d0453aagccf9g434cga3d5g3eaca78cbfaf": ["Stop! I give up! M-mercy, please!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "85489fa7-5691-bc83-204a-2bfb9277b45c"], "h8a1d0f1eg773dg482bgb7a3g8565264508eb": ["I know things, if you l-let me live, I'll make it worth your while. I p-promise!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "6260f7ff-bbc1-31f5-e4dd-86b4bbf76611"], "h73da2c68g6c5cg460ag9ed3g64091c36ce3b": ["Mizora - the prisoner at your camp. <i>Where is she?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "71e59c19-1b81-6403-0e56-02751c752b2b"], "h4f49ac6fgded0g4488g947cg043f6e1e483e": ["The lady Spike nabbed? Drow hauled 'er to Moonrise - jus' over the mountain pass!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "c0023f96-50ac-3eb5-d3cb-b1e0a2ae848c"], "h1596b410g463dg4b71gaf9fg6916ab93c635": ["Now let me go. You got what you wanted!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "5010a0d3-4a66-6c61-46c8-2dad437970b9"], "h09e859d4g095eg488bgb198gcc35593d238e": ["No - you've taken enough lives. It's time I took yours.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "47e61a80-9592-cb72-2e77-52d38c17a410"], "h95ae329fg3b59g40bbgac46gd0d615b61f72": ["Spike - the bruiser. <i>Where is he?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "1e4ece6b-62b8-da2c-b12e-ab3581199523"], "hd5c0feceg744bg452eg8856gd48cde444f83": ["The c-camp. East-ways. Spike's prob'ly gettin' his jollies in the torture-cell.", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "1f79943c-2fa7-3539-9064-870350b6f91c"], "h8832a424ge862g4305g9f92g42e4f14e5fae": ["You sure I c-can't just leave?", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "8e030a79-11d4-bce6-36c5-c664b2f53dcf"], "h94cf90cdg1efag4cf1gadd8gd66086266c7f": ["On your feet, cockroach. Your reckoning's come.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "2170decb-507c-ce4c-1a6f-e47657306bff"], "he36ded11g09aeg4b5bgba31gc7eff79cc8b4": ["<i>Rouse the goblin.</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "4865369f-b216-fce4-4cd8-cfbc0f865887"], "hdd29389fgf15eg4c16gb559g3d9512dfe887": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill_OM_Wyll_AOM_OOM.html", "ad805c17-7dcf-0914-a7ab-0b9a5526e4d0"]}